org.jetel.util

Class TrackingMetadataToolkit

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.util.TrackingMetadataToolkit

  • public class TrackingMetadataToolkit
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is simple toolkit for generation and manipulation with tracking metadata and records. Tracking metadata are artificial data structure containg all tracking information of a graph. For conversion a TrasnformationGraph to tracking metadata call #createMetadadata(TransformationGraph). GraphTacking object can be used also for generation of tracking metadata via invocation of #createMetadadata(GraphTracking) method. Tracking data record can be populated based on GraphTracking object using populateTrackingRecord(DataRecord, GraphTracking) method.
